    "description": "<div id=\"WACViewPanel_ClipboardElement\" class=\"WACEditing EditMode EditingSurfaceBody FireFox WACViewPanel_DisableLegacyKeyCodeAndCharCode usehover\" style=\"overflow: hidden; visibility: visible; direction: ltr;\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW84630876 BCX2\" style=\"direction: ltr;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW84630876 BCX2\" style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; margin: 7.8px 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW84630876 BCX2\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Ars Magica Text\" data-ccp-parastyle-defn=\"{\"ObjectId\":\"2ed15b52-7773-4ee3-b93d-e7ada26e7fc4|221\",\"ClassId\":1073872969,\"Properties\":[469777841,\"Times New Roman\",469777843,\"Times New Roman\",469777844,\"Times New Roman\",469769226,\"Times New Roman\",268442635,\"24\",469777842,\"Times New Roman\",469775450,\"Ars Magica Text\",201340122,\"2\",134233614,\"true\",469778129,\"ArsMagicaText\",335572020,\"99\",335559738,\"117\",469778324,\"Normal\"]}\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman, 'Times New Roman_EmbeddedFont', 'Times New Roman_MSFontService', serif\">The character always knows precisely how to get from where she is to </span></span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW84630876 BCX2\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Ars Magica Text\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman, 'Times New Roman_EmbeddedFont', 'Times New Roman_MSFontService', serif\">a number of locations equal to her Intelligence Score (a minimum of 1). To add a location to the character’s repertoire she must be at that location, the location must be open to the air (so it cannot be inside, for example), and the player must make an Intelligence + Concentration Roll against an Ease Factor of 6. If this would increase the number of known locations beyond the character’s limit, then another location must be “forgotten.” </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman, 'Times New Roman_EmbeddedFont', 'Times New Roman_MSFontService', serif\"> </span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW84630876 BCX2\" style=\"direction: ltr;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW84630876 BCX2\" style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; margin: 7.8px 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-indent: 0px\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW84630876 BCX2\" data-ccp-parastyle=\"Ars Magica Text\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman, 'Times New Roman_EmbeddedFont', 'Times New Roman_MSFontService', serif\">In addition, the character has a fixed Arcane Connection to locations that she knows, which may be exploited in the usual ways (page @@). This Arcane Connection is an artifact of the mind, and so may not be given to another character.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman, 'Times New Roman_EmbeddedFont', 'Times New Roman_MSFontService', serif\"> </span></p></div></div>",
